---
layout: base
title: Submit a Piece
description: Guidelines for pitching and submitting work to The Freethinking Times.
permalink: /submit/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">
  <div class="container--prose">

    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-6); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-ink);">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.815rem); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Submit a Piece</h1>
      <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-style: italic; max-width: 55ch;">
        We read everything. Read these guidelines before you write.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">

      <h2>What We Publish</h2>

      <p>We are interested in reported news, long-form analysis, opinion with a clear argument, cultural criticism, and historical essays that illuminate the present. We are not interested in personal essays that are primarily about the writer, content marketing in any form, or work that has been published elsewhere.</p>

      <p>We value: specificity over generality, evidence over assertion, original reporting over aggregation, and intellectual honesty about uncertainty. We are a small publication and we publish selectively. We would rather run one excellent piece than five adequate ones.</p>

      <h2>How to Pitch</h2>

      <p>Use the form below or email <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> with "Pitch:" at the start of the subject line. A pitch should be under 400 words.</p>

      <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="w3f" style="margin: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-10);">
        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="{{ site.forms.accessKey }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Pitch submission — {{ site.title }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="{{ site.url }}/thank-you/">
        <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="{{ site.title }} Pitch Form">
        <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="visually-hidden" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">

        <div class="w3f__row">
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="pitch-name">Your name <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="text" name="name" id="pitch-name" required aria-required="true" autocomplete="name">
          </div>
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="pitch-email">Email <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="email" name="email" id="pitch-email" required aria-required="true" autocomplete="email">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="pitch-section">Proposed section</label>
          <select class="w3f__select" name="section" id="pitch-section">
            <option value="News">News</option>
            <option value="Opinion">Opinion</option>
            <option value="Analysis">Analysis</option>
            <option value="Arts & Culture">Arts & Culture</option>
            <option value="Science & Technology">Science & Technology</option>
            <option value="History">History</option>
            <option value="Letters">Letters to the Editor</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="pitch-headline">Proposed headline <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
          <input class="w3f__input" type="text" name="headline" id="pitch-headline" required aria-required="true">
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="pitch-body">Your pitch <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
          <span class="w3f__hint" id="pitch-body-hint">What is the piece about? Why does it matter? What evidence will you use? Estimated word count? (Under 400 words)</span>
          <textarea class="w3f__textarea" name="pitch" id="pitch-body" rows="8" required aria-required="true" aria-describedby="pitch-body-hint" maxlength="3000"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="pitch-clips">Published work <span class="w3f__optional">(optional)</span></label>
          <span class="w3f__hint" id="pitch-clips-hint">Link to one or two examples of your published writing</span>
          <input class="w3f__input" type="url" name="clips" id="pitch-clips" placeholder="https://" inputmode="url" aria-describedby="pitch-clips-hint">
        </div>

        <div class="h-captcha" data-captcha="true"></div>
        <button type="submit" class="w3f__submit">Submit Pitch</button>
        <p class="w3f__privacy">We respond to pitches that interest us within two weeks. If you have not heard from us by then, we are passing.</p>
      </form>

      <h2>If We Accept Your Piece</h2>

      <p>We will agree on scope, angle, length, and deadline before you write. We edit actively — expect substantive editorial engagement, not copyediting only. We will not publish a piece without the writer's agreement to the final version.</p>

      <p>Copyright remains with the author. We ask for a thirty-day exclusive before the piece appears elsewhere in substantially similar form.</p>

      <h2>Compensation</h2>

      <p>{{ site.title }} is an independent, self-funded publication with no revenue. We cannot offer payment at this time. Contributors retain full copyright and are free to republish their work after the exclusivity window. We are transparent about this because we believe writers deserve honesty, not euphemism.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
